# Thailand Localization

Singapore portal structure and wording stay unchanged. Localize only operational and commercial data.

## Allowed differences from Singapore

Only these may differ:

- Outlet name
- Outlet code
- Address
- Opening hours
- Last order time
- Product availability
- Thailand pricing
- Currency (THB)
- Payment methods
- Legal information

Everything else must match Singapore.

## Locale defaults

- Country: Thailand
- Brand: Ladurée Thailand
- Timezone: Asia/Bangkok
- Date format: DD/MM/YYYY
- Time format: 24-hour

## Currency and pricing

- Currency: THB only
- Display format: ฿1,290 (or THB 1,290 when that form is required)
- Never display SGD
- Never convert Singapore prices with an exchange rate
- Use only owner-supplied or approved Thailand retail prices

## Content ownership

Outlet details, hours, last-order times, availability, prices, payment methods, and legal/policy text must be supplied or approved by the project owner.

If Thailand-specific data is missing: stop and ask for approval. Do not invent values.
